Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.87,0:02:10.40,note2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs60\pos(90,45)}岛上多处发生火灾
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.51,0:02:10.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三架贝希摩斯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.83,0:02:12.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它们登陆也只是时间问题
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.99,0:02:14.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,AS队情况如何
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.05,0:02:16.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经处于待命状态了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.56,0:02:19.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好 由Uruz-1自行判断进攻时机
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.23,0:02:22.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了吗 克鲁佐上尉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.29,0:02:23.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.79,0:02:28.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Uruz-1呼叫各单位 你们也听到了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.71,0:02:33.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先由Uruz-3/5/8负责攻击贝希摩斯B
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.91,0:02:35.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剩下两架呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.73,0:02:38.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,按预定计划 由我和Uruz-2单独处理
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.27,0:02:40.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我负责贝希摩斯C
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.25,0:02:42.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贝希摩斯A交给Uruz-2
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.49,0:02:44.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,收到了吗 毛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.35,0:02:46.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Uruz-2收到
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.03,0:02:49.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会好好疼爱它的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.48,0:02:50.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尽量争取时间
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.67,0:02:53.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克鲁兹等人将趁机解决贝希摩斯B
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.79,0:02:55.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但愿顺利吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.33,0:02:57.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敌军已越界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.22,0:03:00.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,允许无限制使用ITCC统合战术通信管制系统
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.09,0:03:02.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Uruz-2 收到
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.20,0:03:04.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.38,0:03:41.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先送一份见面礼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.47,0:03:49.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接着是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.69,0:04:18.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,λ-Driver
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.56,0:04:20.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然常规打击都会被挡掉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.35,0:04:24.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然而对出其不意的攻击就无法应对了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.60,0:04:32.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有效果
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.77,0:04:38.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是Uruz-2 已对目标造成轻微损伤
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.25,0:04:39.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,方法可行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.19,0:04:40.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是Perth-1
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.60,0:04:42.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敌军空降部队正在接近
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.95,0:04:45.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若让它们着陆 会演变成白刃战
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.93,0:04:49.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必须尽快使贝希摩斯丧失战力并将其排除
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.71,0:04:51.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,否则我们将全军覆没
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.83,0:04:55.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丧失战力？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.36,0:04:56.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说得倒轻松…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.57,0:05:23.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是Uruz-2
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.86,0:05:25.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遭到贝希摩斯A的还击
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.78,0:05:28.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将变更观测地点后继续迎击
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.77,0:05:30.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别死啊 大姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.86,0:05:32.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Uruz-8呼叫Uruz-6
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.92,0:05:35.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 怕了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.49,0:05:37.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,胡说八道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.15,0:05:40.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,指挥权已经交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.11,0:05:44.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是给你当诱饵了 你可别坑我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.51,0:05:45.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.08,0:05:49.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说 克鲁兹
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.58,0:05:50.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.06,0:05:53.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当时泰莎是真的准备…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.12,0:05:56.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.55,0:05:59.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 当我没说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.07,0:06:02.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她不会开枪的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.99,0:06:04.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为她不是那种女生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.95,0:06:05.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.25,0:06:08.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 换成我肯定开枪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.15,0:06:10.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.65,0:06:12.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,准备上了 Uruz-8
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.33,0:06:14.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,随时可以
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.73,0:06:15.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Uruz-5
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.97,0:06:17.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.77,0:06:18.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Uruz-3
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.15,0:06:20.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,准备就绪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.69,0:06:22.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好…开始吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.71,0:06:24.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妖精之眼启动
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.88,0:06:31.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这玩意真好用
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.76,0:06:34.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它开始防范水中的自航水雷了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.68,0:06:39.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个λ-Driver能防御一切攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.85,0:06:41.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你确定吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.24,0:06:41.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.99,0:06:44.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是它也有弱点
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.87,0:06:47.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是只能朝预先戒备的方向产生力场
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.61,0:06:49.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偷袭就会有效吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.29,0:06:49.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.91,0:06:53.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那它的要害…驾驶舱在哪儿
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.56,0:06:54.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,头部
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.90,0:06:58.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但想要一击制敌是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.41,0:07:00.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 按目前情况看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.31,0:07:04.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,M9的装备无法击穿它的复合装甲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.03,0:07:06.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.41,0:07:07.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一发是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.98,0:07:14.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少要连续两发76MM弹精确命中同一点
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.47,0:07:16.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样应该有效
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.33,0:07:18.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.53,0:07:21.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偷袭似乎能扰乱λ-Driver的展开
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.89,0:07:24.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是机会只有一次
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.87,0:07:26.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一旦对方有所防范就再无机会
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.20,0:07:31.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太扯了吧  不可能成功的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.97,0:07:34.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我又开始想投降了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.71,0:07:36.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可不一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.07,0:07:39.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说不定能行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.28,0:07:41.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有什么计划吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.60,0:07:43.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.37,0:07:46.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像穿过针眼一样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.37,0:07:48.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,按计划行事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.99,0:07:50.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三重佯攻
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.96,0:07:55.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,倒数 3 2 1
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.70,0:07:57.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Alpha 上！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.26,0:08:34.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Beta 上！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.71,0:08:50.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尝尝这个！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.17,0:09:10.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 分散了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.97,0:09:13.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Gamma 上！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.50,0:09:15.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Uruz-3 收到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.30,0:09:51.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该死 失手了！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.60,0:10:04.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,规避！规避！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.27,0:10:09.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还用得着你说！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.95,0:10:15.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中招了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.48,0:10:17.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,束手无策了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.15,0:10:19.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,万事休矣了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.00,0:10:20.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还没完！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.12,0:10:23.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,斯贝克
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.35,0:10:27.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,继续坚持 我再给你创造一次机会
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.68,0:10:29.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再来一次！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.04,0:10:42.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然这不是我的风格
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.01,0:10:46.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,够了！快撤！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.61,0:10:49.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,替我向上校道个歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.43,0:10:51.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.69,0:11:01.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事…该死！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.62,0:11:14.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我并没有真的想要出卖…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.51,0:11:23.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,斯贝克！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.98,0:11:28.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.03,0:11:31.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.44,0:12:10.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,斯贝克…你这个大傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.23,0:12:31.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)}（地雷启动）
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.12,0:12:46.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好歹能拖延一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.35,0:12:47.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是Uruz-6
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.39,0:12:50.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已成功击毁贝希摩斯B
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.45,0:12:52.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Uruz-8阵亡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.01,0:13:04.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是Uruz-2 步枪子弹用尽了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.01,0:13:05.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毛？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.35,0:13:07.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Uruz-2！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.17,0:13:07.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毛！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.69,0:13:13.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事 我还有这个
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.28,0:13:19.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会尽量争取时间
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.53,0:13:21.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们先去解决掉贝希摩斯C
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.49,0:13:25.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.88,0:13:30.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,探测到S2区域有大量飞行部队 方位204
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.85,0:13:33.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,空降部队登场了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.20,0:14:28.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呼叫各单位 收到请回话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.26,0:14:30.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人能听见吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.26,0:14:41.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结束了吗…该死
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.81,0:14:54.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还活着吗 Uruz-2
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.89,0:14:56.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡斯泰洛中尉！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.25,0:14:57.69,note2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs60\pos(90,45)}不行 快离开
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.76,0:14:58.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闭嘴 给我乖乖地…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.70,0:15:03.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中尉！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.93,0:15:08.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中尉！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.17,0:15:12.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来当诱饵
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.39,0:15:15.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你快弃机逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.04,0:15:15.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太乱来了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.53,0:15:18.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是命令！快走 少尉！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.30,0:15:26.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放马过来 怪物！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.77,0:15:35.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡斯泰洛中尉！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.05,0:16:21.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Uruz-5受损严重
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.37,0:16:23.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,驾驶员疑似受重伤
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.48,0:16:25.67,note2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs60\pos(90,45)}敌军从T3空域降落
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.23,0:16:26.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,PRT第二单位损失惨重
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.72,0:16:28.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三人死亡 八人重伤
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.13,0:16:29.66,note2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs60\pos(90,45)}Gebo-7 无响应
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.41,0:16:31.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敌军空降部队已抵达
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.73,0:16:33.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我们奋力抵抗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.77,0:16:35.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但最多也只能撑30分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.85,0:16:38.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还需要两个小时才能用De Danaan撤离
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.49,0:16:42.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白 但30分钟已经是极限了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.21,0:16:44.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.03,0:16:49.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请讲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.28,0:16:52.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中止填充反应堆
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.47,0:16:55.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剩余人员全部派去检测水密系统
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.70,0:16:59.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来只能这么做了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.70,0:17:00.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,收到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.39,0:17:02.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上校…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.74,0:17:04.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算我们成功撤离了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.60,0:17:06.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也只能航行两周吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.20,0:17:09.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但这是唯一的选择了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.52,0:17:11.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.46,0:17:16.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少校…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.41,0:17:18.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上校！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.74,0:17:20.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Uruz-6呼叫
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.30,0:17:21.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接过来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.37,0:17:22.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是Uruz-6
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.05,0:17:25.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目前仍在与贝希摩斯A交战
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.37,0:17:27.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然还没有击毁
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.13,0:17:29.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但已经消耗了对方大量弹药
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.54,0:17:31.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡斯泰洛中尉阵亡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.15,0:17:32.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毛也下落不明
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.14,0:17:36.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,收到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.49,0:17:38.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请先返回基地
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.45,0:17:41.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 另一支空降部队正在接近
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.74,0:17:43.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我再坚持一会
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.93,0:17:45.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Uruz-6
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.25,0:17:47.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的剩余弹药应该也不多了 立即返回
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.67,0:17:48.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,威巴中士！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.84,0:17:49.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,威巴中士！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.71,0:17:56.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不这样的话 就没脸见他们了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.22,0:18:03.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Uruz-6快回答 听不到吗！Uruz-6！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.21,0:18:05.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.26,0:18:16.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那样做也不合适吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.81,0:18:19.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可结果还是自习了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.53,0:18:22.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs60\an8}（第二节古典B因教师紧急会议改为自习）
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.53,0:18:22.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干脆停课算了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.98,0:18:25.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然不知道是恐袭还是事故
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.53,0:18:29.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早知道一开始就翘课了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.64,0:18:30.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.89,0:18:33.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相良同学和千鸟同学都请假了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.85,0:18:35.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是出什么事了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.56,0:18:38.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁知道呢 话说常盘也没来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.65,0:18:39.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打过电话了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.85,0:18:41.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打了啊 没人接
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.89,0:18:42.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.88,0:18:45.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不知道她在干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.10,0:18:53.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小妹妹 这事怪不得你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.79,0:18:58.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为是工作需要
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.45,0:19:00.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也觉得很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.55,0:19:03.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道那个是什么吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.39,0:19:07.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 是炸弹
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.49,0:19:11.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学校各处都布置了这玩意
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.99,0:19:15.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要是挣扎或者呼救的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.49,0:19:18.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的许多朋友都会陪你上路
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.63,0:19:19.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果不想这种事发生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.99,0:19:21.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就得乖乖听话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.33,0:19:28.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.72,0:19:30.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目标跟丢了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.66,0:19:33.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们在继续监听警方无线电和通讯线路
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.21,0:19:35.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,继续监视
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.41,0:19:39.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他不会不顾朋友死活 独自逃命的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.93,0:19:41.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能会逃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.15,0:19:44.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给您造成的不便请多见谅
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.87,0:19:48.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由于今日凌晨发生的大规模通讯故障
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.75,0:19:51.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们将设立紧急检查站
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.69,0:20:27.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实我知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.57,0:20:32.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之前的生活不会一直持续下去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.14,0:20:34.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终有一天敌人会到来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.83,0:20:36.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切都会变得一团糟
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.75,0:20:41.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早在半年前就已经得出结论了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.66,0:20:44.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是你的错
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.53,0:20:46.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好害怕…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.48,0:20:50.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怕他们 也怕自己的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.39,0:20:54.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最近 越来越多从未了解过的知识涌入脑中
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.29,0:20:59.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就仿佛我不再是我自己了一样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.91,0:21:02.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千鸟…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.99,0:21:05.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.59,0:21:08.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 我也怕你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.17,0:21:10.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然喜欢你 但还是害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.61,0:21:13.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然无法自拔地喜欢你 但还是害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.77,0:21:16.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经搞不懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.33,0:21:21.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.49,0:21:25.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.86,0:21:29.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但也惧怕你 无法理解你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.21,0:21:31.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使如此 我仍旧被你所吸引
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.23,0:21:34.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从第一次相遇起 就一直重复这个循环
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.66,0:21:38.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你改变了我的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.94,0:21:41.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宗介…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.62,0:21:43.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我曾想过和你远走高飞
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.54,0:21:46.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但如果只有我们俩是没有意义的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.82,0:21:51.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和学校的同学一起欢笑生气的你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.58,0:21:53.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才是我所需要的
